⚠️ IMPORTANT NOTE (VERY IMPORTANT)

👉 JSON used in AWS does NOT support comments

So:

✅ For GitHub (documentation purpose)

✔ You can keep comments (like above)

❌ For AWS S3 console

👉 You must remove comments:
{
  "Version": "2012-10-17",
  "Statement": [
    {
      "Sid": "PublicReadAccess", 
      // This statement allows public read access to all objects in the bucket

      "Effect": "Allow",
      // Allow the action

      "Principal": "*",
      // '*' means anyone on the internet can access (public)

      "Action": "s3:GetObject",
      // Only allows reading/downloading files (safe for static websites)

      "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::nancymishrawebsite/*"
      // IMPORTANT: Replace with your bucket name
      // Format: arn:aws:s3:::<your-bucket-name>/*
    }
  ]
}

